Given a scoring system for vertices, network hubs are defined as the vertices whose score is significantly higher than others (\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
